   <body>
      <p>The Incentive Program Manager has Billing as the Program Type.</p>
      <p>The Billing Program has the following default program sub-types with the Administrator/Super User created program sub-types in Active status:</p>
      <ul>
         <li>Month End Billing Program</li>
         <li>Reward Saving Program</li>
         <li>Package Saving Program</li>
         <li>Bundle Saving Program</li>
         <li>Partnership Saving Program</li>
      </ul>
